data.description: Priced to Sale! Location Location Location. Ready for Move-in! The 2 story 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath with a large backyard has been Freshly Painted with New carpet installed upstairs. The downstairs living area has a fireplace with an eat-in kitchen. The bedrooms are upstairs with a Flex/Game Room. This home is in the desirable Sonoma Ranch Neighborhood minutes from 1604 and Hausman. The large flat backyard has a storage shed and has great potential for an entertainment oasis with green space between you the backyard neighbor. Convenient to 1604, La Cantera, HEB plus, Fiesta Texas, and so much more. Great NISD schools.
